{"word":"Thorn","slug":"thorn","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Thorn</b> The ground cursed with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=18'>Gen 3:18</a><br/> Used as an awl<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=41&verse=2'>Job 41:2</a><br/> Used for fuel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=58&verse=9'>Psa 58:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=118&verse=12'>Psa 118:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=7&verse=6'>Ecc 7:6</a><br/> Hedges formed of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=2&verse=6'>Hos 2:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=7&verse=4'>Mic 7:4</a><br/> Crown of, mockingly put on Jesus' head<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=29'>Mat 27:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=17'>Mar 15:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=2'>Joh 19:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=5'>Joh 19:5</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of afflictions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=55'>Num 33:55</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=12&verse=7'>2Co 12:7</a> <br/> - Of the adversities of the wicked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=22&verse=5'>Pro 22:5</a> <br/> - Of the evils that spring from the heart to choke the truth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=7'>Mat 13:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=22'>Mat 13:22</a> "}]}